  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a wok or large frying pan over medium heat.",
    "Add leeks, shallots, and garlic to the heated oil. Cook until softened.",
    "Add tomato paste and cook for an additional minute, stirring continuously.",
    "Increase heat to high, add lamb mince and red wine vinegar, stir well.",
    "Cook for 3-4 minutes or until mince is browned and cooked through.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste. Add fresh dill if using.",
    "Serve hot as a main course."
